National Grid May Sell Niagara Mohawk Unit, Mail on Sunday Says

-- B y   M i c h e l l e   E .   F r a z e r
-- 
2011-05-22T07:50:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-22/national-grid-may-sell-niagara-mohawk-unit-mail-on-sunday-says.html
National Grid Plc (NG/)  may sell its
Niagara Mohawk Power Corp. unit for more than 1 billion pounds
($1.6 billion), the Mail on Sunday reported, without saying
where it got the information.  Barclays Capital and Merrill Lynch are helping National
Grid with a strategic review, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michelle E. Frazer in London at 
 mfrazer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  